# No slide footers

- Do not add footer titles, deck names, partner names, page numbers, or total-page counts to slides.
- Do not introduce or use footer components whose purpose is to render this metadata.
- When editing an existing page, leave unrelated legacy footers unchanged unless the user asks to remove them.
